Class MapGraphRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • bean.pwr.imskamieskiego.repository.MapGraphRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMapGraphRepository

    public class MapGraphRepository
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMapGraphRepository
    This class is implementation of IMapGraphRepository. It should be used to get access to data related to graph. Methods of this class must be call from thread other than main thread.
